summary: This document is an invoice from FedEx detailing charges for services rendered on July 9, 2001. It includes transportation charges, special handling charges, and payment details for NYSG LLC, with a total amount due of $27.04. The invoice also mentions changes to the process for requesting invoice adjustments.
keyFacts: The invoice includes a fuel surcharge of $1.04.
The package was picked up on July 9, 2001, and delivered on July 10, 2001.
